WEBVTT

00:14:57.896 --> 00:15:00.325
When I was leading
the turnaround at Gatorade,

00:15:00.349 --> 00:15:02.422
for a period of 18 months,

00:15:02.446 --> 00:15:05.850
our results were so incredibly
embarrassingly bad,

00:15:05.874 --> 00:15:10.630
that you know, I think daily
I was expecting to get fired.

00:15:10.654 --> 00:15:14.773
And because I'd been through this before,

00:15:14.797 --> 00:15:21.539
it gave me just this incredibly deep
reservoir of courage to keep going,

00:15:21.563 --> 00:15:25.554
because I just knew
that even if they fire me,

00:15:25.578 --> 00:15:26.746
I'm going to be OK,

00:15:26.770 --> 00:15:28.620
because I've been through that before.

00:15:28.943 --> 00:15:31.332
